<h3 id="paper-style">Paper Style</h3>
<p>The HIPS paper style is identical to the IPDPS paper style. Submitted manuscripts may not exceed 10 single-spaced double-column pages using 10-point size font on 8.5x11 inch pages (IEEE conference style), including figures, tables, and references.</p>
